{"tid":582532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★要發財，齊齊來幹香港IT行業吧！","createTime":"2018-03-06T09:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-08T15:00:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ff9b126d19e6b531e871e1b6decfe2ede6e757ba","tid":582532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:05:58.000Z","msg":"發展科技乃全球大勢所趨，不少企業紛紛投身創科領域，對相關人才的需求亦愈來愈大。香港科技園公司日前便舉行了職業博覽，場內提供逾千職位空缺，當中不乏本地、區域性或國際性企業，吸引超過5000名求職者踴躍參與。最特別的是，博覽首次舉辦「60秒求職擂台」環節，獲得機會的求職者於台上用一分鐘時間介紹自己，吸引招聘企業的注目，增加受聘機會。創科公司提醒職場新鮮人，如有意投身創科界，必須具備創新精神，並對於市場及產業發展有自己一套，全程投入為創科發展出力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180306/bkn-20180306083015365-0306_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180306%2Fbkn-20180306083015365-0306_00822_001.html&d=AiK%2FvUy3SAFDSmMwJ3%2B86zOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2d5c81b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180306/bkn-20180306083015365-0306_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c5e3da3568597b3a87af702ccd6c29407321d831","tid":582532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T09:06:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/170622_e267f6e8ba4b2a9359a63b1b01b33454.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F170622_e267f6e8ba4b2a9359a63b1b01b33454.png&h=ebe48ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/170624_dce36f0797a1654eefe909f1052572ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F170624_dce36f0797a1654eefe909f1052572ac.png&h=020d71aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/06/170625_ac9eaa7fa26a4cb3e7390eb9973fc490.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F06%2F170625_ac9eaa7fa26a4cb3e7390eb9973fc